{"tid":813484,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓爆2018】震驚！新盤買家單幢盤撻訂損失472萬！賣方勁減超過700萬跪求重賣！","createTime":"2018-09-10T12:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T08:00:20.000Z","uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"229b88ccd0334c3933bb18d0a415a9b4e9128788","tid":813484,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"新盤再現撻定。華懋九龍城單幢盤御‧豪門，60樓D室連天台特色戶，實用面積1,619方呎，今年6月以4,716.47萬元連兩個車位(各值300萬元)成交，呎價29,132元，買家已簽定正式買賣合約，但最終撻定，料被發展商沒收最少一成定金，損失約472萬元。土地註冊處資料顯示，撻定買家為潘啟明(POON KAI MING)，與一名骨科專科醫生同名。<br />\n<br />\n發展商表示，該撻定貨剛以4,000萬元重售，不連車位，60天成交。單位早前連兩個車位曾以價單形式售出，當時售價4,716.47萬元，並選用首20個月免息按揭付款計劃。若同樣以60天成交期付款計劃比較，是次標售價較價單售價高約0.4%。<br />\n<br />\n記者:朱連峰<br />\n<br />\n全球樓行 Dream House零距離<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&d=h9x%2FkiD%2Fjg6zPxWSC06eAghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=054ffd92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&h=9bc132df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty</a>"},{"pid":"8260ed6ce6a5da52ce0b06cc9103bcbbdf6dd9d4","tid":813484,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"4000 萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987a68be6336580da35d397a4a9549ae61df425a","tid":813484,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8260ed6ce6a5da52ce0b06cc9103bcbbdf6dd9d4","tid":813484,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"4000 萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:03:31.000Z","msg":"減700萬，樓爆了"},{"pid":"5dcd0c4919f1b491d4d8a07499367aecd6c5a71a","tid":813484,"uid":145779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T